{"title":"搬离三峡","authors":["向求纬"],"dates":[{"year":2000,"month":9,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬离三峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向求纬"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬离三峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不等于告别三峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是整个儿"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"连根拔起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"所以心口隐隐地痛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我不知道祖先"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当年是怎样走进三峡"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一叶扁舟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条纤索"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪儿栽下木桩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪儿就是家"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这家就骑在波浪上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这家就挂在岩壁上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这家在峡江淘了多年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴落了不少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晾干了不少"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"按照惯例"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"搬离三峡的时候"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总要带走一抔泥土"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块卵石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带走关于故乡的记忆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"门前的三峡越来越远"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"梦中的三峡越来越近"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一不留神"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过滤的心田里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就会浮出一个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"湿漉漉的家"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":12,"page_end":12}